{"url":"https://www.aqa-co.com/contact/","html":"<!doctype html>\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/vnd.microsoft.icon\" href=\"/common/images/favicon.ico\">\n<title>お問い合わせ | アクア警備保障株式会社｜アクア警備保障株式会社</title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"アクア警備保障ヘのお問い合わせは、お問い合わせフォームを活用してください。\">\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"警備,交通誘導警備,雑踏警備,イベント警備,列車見張警備,保安警備,巡回警備\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/common/css/base.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/common/css/contact.css\">\n<!--[if lt IE 9]>\n        <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://html5shim.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js\"></script>\n        <![endif]-->\n<style>\nheader, footer, nav, section, article, figure, aside {\ndisplay: block;\n}\n</style>\n<!-- jQuery -->\n<script src=\"http://www.google.com/jsapi\"></script>\n<script>google.load(\"jquery\", \"1.7.1\");</script>\n<!-- //jQuery -->\n<script src=\"/common/js/jquery.smooth.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/common/js/smartRollover.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/common/js/jquery.dlTableSet.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n$(function(){\n    $('#form dl').dlTableSet();\n});\n</script>\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-GGYDMZ71NT\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n  gtag('config', 'G-GGYDMZ71NT');\n</script>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/contact/common/css/form.css\" />\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"//ajaxzip3.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ajaxzip3/ajaxzip3.js\" charset=\"UTF-8\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.2/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/contact/common/js/jquery.validate.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/contact/common/js/jquery.placeholder.min.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/contact/common/js/form.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n$(function(){\n    $('input[placeholder],textarea[placeholder]').placeholder();\n});\n</script></head>\n<body id=\"contact\">\n<div id=\"header\">\n <div class=\"container\">\n  <h1 id=\"h-logo\"><img src=\"/common/images/img_logo.png\" width=\"315\" height=\"63\" alt=\"アクア警備保障株式会社\"></h1>\n </div>\n</div>\n<!-- //header -->\n<div id=\"contents\">\n<div id=\"main\">\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<h2><img src=\"/common/images/contact/pagetitle.png\" width=\"700\" height=\"100\" alt=\"お問い合わせフォーム\"></h2>\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<div class=\"box\">\n<p>ご相談・ご質問などは、こちらのお問い合わせフォームより承っております。 <br> 折り返し、担当よりご連絡をいたします。 </p>\n</div>\t\n</div>\n<div class=\"wrapper\">\n<div class=\"box\">\n<h3 class=\"blue-b\">【個人情報の取り扱いについて】</h3>\n<p> ご記入いただいた個人情報は、お問い合わせの回答等、必要な範囲で利用させて頂きます。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"txac mat30\" style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\"><img src=\"/common/images/contact/img_flow1.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"40\"  alt=\"入力\"/></div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"alphaform\">\n<form method=\"post\" action=\"confirm.php\">\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr id=\"column_type\">\n<th><span class=\"hissu\">お問い合わせ区分</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"radio\" name=\"type\" id=\"type_1\" value=\"当社について\" class=\"radio required\" /><label for=\"type_1\">当社について</label>\n<input type=\"radio\" name=\"type\" id=\"type_2\" value=\"業務について\" class=\"radio required\" /><label for=\"type_2\">業務について</label>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_name\">\n<th><span class=\"hissu\">お名前</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"\" size=\"30\" class=\"text required zen\" />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_office\">\n<th><span class=\"nini\">会社名</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"office\" id=\"office\" value=\"\" size=\"30\" class=\"text zen\" />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_unit\">\n<th><span class=\"nini\">部署名</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"unit\" id=\"unit\" value=\"\" size=\"30\" class=\"text zen\" />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_zipcode\">\n<th><span class=\"nini\">郵便番号</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"zipcode\" id=\"zipcode\" value=\"\" size=\"8\" onchange=\"AjaxZip3.zip2addr(this, '', 'addr', 'addr');\" class=\"text zip\" maxlength=\"8\" />\n<span class=\"memo_right\">(半角数字)</span><div class=\"memo_bottom\">例）3700002</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_addr\">\n<th><span class=\"nini\">住所</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"addr\" id=\"addr\" value=\"\" size=\"50\" class=\"text\" />\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_tel\">\n<th><span class=\"nini\">電話番号</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"tel\" id=\"tel\" value=\"\" size=\"20\" class=\"text tel\" maxlength=\"15\" />\n<span class=\"memo_right\">(半角英数)</span><div class=\"memo_bottom\">例）027-370-0033</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_mail\">\n<th><span class=\"hissu\">メールアドレス</span></th><td>\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"mail\" id=\"mail\" value=\"\" size=\"40\" class=\"text required email\" maxlength=\"100\" />\n<span class=\"memo_right\">(半角英数)</span><div class=\"memo_bottom\">※フリーメールをご利用の方は、当社からのメールが迷惑メールと選別される場合がございます。<br />※迷惑メールボックスを確認いただくなど、ご注意ください。</div></td>\n</tr>\n<tr id=\"column_message\">\n<th><span class=\"hissu\">お問い合わせ内容</span></th><td>\n<textarea name=\"message\" id=\"message\" cols=\"50\" rows=\"10\" class=\"textarea required\" ></textarea>\n<div class=\"memo_bottom\">※400文字以内でご記入ください。<br />※半角カタカナ、丸数字、特殊文字は使用しないでください。</div></td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"action_button\">\n<input type=\"submit\" name=\"confirm\" value=\"送信内容を確認する\" class=\"button confirm_button\" id=\"submit\" />\n</div>\n</form>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- //main --> \n</div>\n<!-- //contents -->\n<div id=\"footer\">\n <div class=\"container\">\n  <div id=\"address\">\n   <div class=\"footer_logo\">\n    <h2><img src=\"/common/images/img_logo.png\" alt=\"アクア警備保障株式会社\" width=\"315\" height=\"63\"></h2>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"address_text\">\n    <address>\n    〒370-0002　群馬県高崎市日高町394-5 <br> TEL：027-370-0033　FAX：027-370-0034\n    </address>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"copyright-mini clear\" style=\"font-size:80%;\"> Copyright© 2015-2024 aqua security services Co.Ltd,All Rights Reserved. </p>\n </div>\n</div>\n","finalUrl":"https://www.aqa-co.com/contact/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-23T20:42:35.776Z"}